room_title: Escape room "Black Ops" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
room_description:
"Stingray, do you copy? Please advise. Over”
“Affirmative, Viper Team…Warthogs inbound. Wheels up in 60. Over.”
“Copy that, Stingray. Ground troops have diverted all hostile fire away from the bunker…awaiting clearance.”
“Clearance granted, Viper Team…hold position until NICO finds….well, whatever in the hell it is they’re trying to find. “
“Roger that, Stingray….Viper Team, out.”

...That was the last transmission you and your team heard before entering the tunnel.
